Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie put on a “True and Fake Tibbie” show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at Darton’s base camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,rescuing her friends in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After leaving the Bizarre World’s timespace,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,what will they run into next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re back at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so tired. I need to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Another quake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to finish our job as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no time for me to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, at least wait for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Werewolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,we’re here to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s just that the quake tipped over my bookshelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you guys worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay. I’ll help you tidy up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t be too long, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonie,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat gave me this when he saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The others haven’t gone far. Let’s catch up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Werewolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Jonie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The goats?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Werewolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I get rid of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the plan has to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Werewolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t need him anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He threw out Mecha-Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Mecha-Goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Jonie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, you remember me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Origin: Argali Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Height: 1.3 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Weight: Two hundred and—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing you’re okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we take you to the Hub?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I must rescue my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends are here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we’ll take you to the Hub,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we’ll go find your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I must find my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we take him with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Since mechanical goats can sense each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we might just find other anachronists.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission commenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How come neither Weslie nor Jonie have a signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t get in contact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re not in trouble, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, check and see where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie and Jonie should be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing I’m okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Werewolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sparky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t let them ruin my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the one who’s done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,—Magic Airplanes!　—Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the plan, I have to distract them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat, do we keep going straight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The destination is the gorge up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat, do you need any charging?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about I have Rainbow do a full-body check on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hand is dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I help you wipe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maximum power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,give me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes a dragnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, Tibbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,surround his front and back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky and I will surround his left and his right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie and Jonie, surround his top and bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie and Jonie haven’t come back yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of catching me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys better worry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,about Weslie and Jonie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he distract us on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Weslie and Jonie might be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi, check to see if they have a signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m getting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, Jonie, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, Jonie, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do? They’re not inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go find them, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t see any other mechanical goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Found them. They are over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mecha-Goat, are you sure they’re here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong with you, Mecha-Goat?
